Shri Mataji: No, no. It is something like
a light going out and the tube is still there.

51:41.265 --> 51:45.169
It is like that the Kundalini. But it
stays on top of the head of the person.

51:45.369 --> 51:48.539
The only difference is, supposing,
the light goes out and stays near by.

51:48.739 --> 51:52.610
You see the potential is
there in the light. It is like that.

51:52.810 --> 51:55.956
