53:56.437 --> 54:00.504
Yogini: Mataji, you said the
different gurus have different...

54:02.461 --> 54:05.776
the fake gurus have damaged the chakras.

54:07.111 --> 54:13.183
How do they do it? And what’s to be done about it?

54:14.532 --> 54:18.922
Shri Mataji: You see, what gurus do is
they use different chakras

54:19.320 --> 54:26.516
for introducing into the sympathetic nervous system
some entities which they have controlled, you see.

54:26.717 --> 54:30.267
They do not control
many entities as such, but what happens,

54:31.209 --> 54:37.508
for example now I would say, during war many
people died just like that; killed and this and that.

54:37.996 --> 54:41.011
In those countries, those souls,

54:41.211 --> 54:46.895
you see they were never,
sort of - well never had a human life

54:47.095 --> 54:51.622
and they were treated just like animals
and they were very much tortured.

54:51.822 --> 54:56.226
So they had that feeling in their minds
that, “We should also torture these people.”

54:56.593 --> 55:02.933
So when they die they do not die really and
they do not get into the pretloka (Spirit world).

55:03.133 --> 55:06.437
They stay in the atmosphere and
that’s why wars are very bad things,

55:06.637 --> 55:10.038
because wars create such human
beings much more, with accidents and

55:10.239 --> 55:13.243
people who are very
depraved in life, very dissatisfied

55:13.443 --> 55:16.515
who are doing all kinds of depraved actions and

55:16.716 --> 55:21.663
secretive things and all kinds
of horrid things. All such people, all of them,

55:21.863 --> 55:25.599
when they die they do not
really go to pretaloka because

55:25.799 --> 55:30.322
they don’t think of their salvation but
they are just thinking of their lust, greed

55:30.522 --> 55:34.264
or we can say possessions,

55:34.464 --> 55:38.669
those who are grabbing things,
thieves and all sorts of people.

55:39.733 --> 55:44.093
We can call ‘evil’ people and
satanic people, when they die

55:44.293 --> 55:48.312
they find they become much
more subtler and they can be

55:48.512 --> 55:50.865
better off if they act in a subtle body.

55:51.065 --> 55:55.219
So they use the subtle body for acting
into people and such people are easily available.

55:55.419 --> 55:58.692
So these gurus, what they do, that
they themselves are evil geniuses,

55:58.892 --> 56:02.782
and they have a way of capturing
those people and they use them.

56:02.983 --> 56:05.326
And they introduce to you
through your different chakras.

56:05.526 --> 56:10.334
