56:14.435 --> 56:20.210
people should never fight Rama, because at
that time the sensitivity of people was so great

56:20.410 --> 56:23.914
that they knew that Rama was an incarnation.
They were not gross as today they are that,

56:24.114 --> 56:27.034
one has to tell that, “Oh,
here I am the incarnation.”

56:27.235 --> 56:30.419
That time it was not Kali Yuga so
they knew he was an incarnation.

56:30.619 --> 56:35.989
And so many of them, I mean some of them did not,
but quite a lot of them knew and despite that

56:36.189 --> 56:39.261
nobody could oppose it because their,

56:40.102 --> 56:43.925
mind was captured by these entities
put by Ravana and they fought Him.

56:44.126 --> 56:47.971
So, it was so, even at the time of
Krishna: people knew who He was at least

56:48.171 --> 56:50.927
they had quite an idea,
even Kauravas new about it.

56:51.128 --> 56:55.078
But this Kali Yuga is a wretched
thing – nobody see anything clearly.

56:55.278 --> 57:01.537
But those times were not like that. People knew
who was an incarnation and they understood it.

57:01.738 --> 57:06.830
At that time also, these people had to use
some sort of a way of putting them off and

57:07.031 --> 57:09.560
