58:03.847 --> 58:07.150
There are so many things they
do like that: thousand and one.

58:07.741 --> 58:12.456
But human beings, as a whole in the Kali Yuga,

58:12.656 --> 58:16.593
instead of improving has
gone down absolutely in his,

58:17.219 --> 58:21.235
conception of Divinity and in everything.

58:21.436 --> 58:26.713
I mean he’s a hopeless case otherwise! But
