58:26.914 --> 58:30.707
They way it is I mean he’s very, very blunt.

58:30.907 --> 58:37.481
He cannot seek, he’s very insensitive.
And he carries on all kinds of his malpractices

58:37.681 --> 58:43.854
thinking that he’s a rare saint ever born.
