59:04.411 --> 59:08.014
Ata dusra prashna (marathi: now another question)

59:24.441 --> 59:29.266
Yogi: How music works on the five chakras?

59:30.774 --> 59:33.695
Shri Mataji: You see all these five elements

59:33.896 --> 59:37.941
are very important in our body and they

59:38.141 --> 59:41.220
are the body of the chakras
also as I have told you.

59:41.421 --> 59:44.881
So what happens that, when you sing the music,

59:45.081 --> 59:51.816
the vibrations can go through the musical
sound and can excite certain chakras.

59:52.017 --> 59:55.805
You see for example for the
hriday (heart) chakra is very good

59:56.005 --> 59:59.763
or also for the Vishuddhi chakra it is very good.

59:59.963 --> 01:00:02.680
Not for all the
chakras. But certain chakras it does.

01:00:02.880 --> 01:00:08.071
But supposing you say a mantra
that’s the sound, with beautiful music

01:00:08.271 --> 01:00:11.308
and a realised soul then
it is very effective, you see.

01:00:11.508 --> 01:00:17.376
For example, Ganesha you can
excite him with a beautiful sloka

01:00:17.576 --> 01:00:23.754
if you are a realised soul and if your Ganesha is correct,
you can excite the Ganesha of another person very easily,

01:00:23.977 --> 01:00:30.101
I mean such a person do it. So music,
sound, all these things have an effect and

01:00:30.302 --> 01:00:36.274
we are now using that method very extensively.
But supposing now, we go in a mass meditation and

01:00:36.474 --> 01:00:40.037
many people are there and some
chakra is caught, say Vishuddhi is caught,

01:00:40.238 --> 01:00:43.607
I can correct their Vishuddhi by just
putting My finger on this, like this,

01:00:43.807 --> 01:00:51.018
because this has the sound, this is in the chakras, there
is a micro-sound which is carrying the vibrations, you see.

01:00:51.218 --> 01:00:56.297
Actually the part of the vibrations is the
micro-sound also, micro-light, micro-sound

01:00:56.498 --> 01:00:59.023
and you can say all the five elements are
micro there.

01:00:59.223 --> 01:01:03.827
So when I put my finger the micro sound can carry
the rest of them and the person can be corrected.

01:01:04.027 --> 01:01:07.518
We can do it. Specially Vishuddhi.
Very easy to correct Vishuddhi on that.

01:01:07.719 --> 01:01:11.735
You can correct most of the things but
certain things are very easily corrected.

01:01:11.935 --> 01:01:19.910
Vishuddhi, which is responsible for the
sound, made from the sound element.

01:01:21.022 --> 01:01:28.779
As we have seen that water element is very
good for treating people for the lower chakras,

01:01:28.980 --> 01:01:36.301
because up to the heart chakra, because the
water and salt can help you for the Nabhi chakra

01:01:36.501 --> 01:01:41.698
and because salt is the earth element

01:01:41.898 --> 01:01:46.636
and what do you call it?
It is essence of the ocean and

01:01:46.836 --> 01:01:52.609
the essence of the ocean is in the bhavasagara. So
we can use salt water for clearing the lower chakras.

01:01:52.809 --> 01:02:00.050
We can use light for the eyes because,
this is made out of the prakash – light element.

01:02:00.250 --> 01:02:03.987
Like that different things can be done.

01:02:04.964 --> 01:02:12.963
And with these different elements if you use them, you can
make all the dirt or all the obstructions, which are collected,

01:02:13.163 --> 01:02:19.102
in your particular chakra by putting
them back into the same element

01:02:19.302 --> 01:02:22.539
and cleansing
them out so the element takes it away.

01:02:22.739 --> 01:02:28.210
For Mother Earth also, She has so many elements in
Her that She can take away so many of your problems

01:02:28.410 --> 01:02:31.867
which are troubling you, in your being,

01:02:32.068 --> 01:02:37.521
because of some imbalance
of the Mother Earth element.

01:02:38.180 --> 01:02:45.829
You see, this is all due to the imbalance of these elements
in you, accumulated more beyond than what you want it.

01:02:46.029 --> 01:02:48.611
That’s why I said, “the extreme of it.”

01:02:51.314 --> 01:02:55.611
Prithvi tattwa (earth element)
is expressed through Shri Ganesh

01:02:55.811 --> 01:02:59.679
and Shri Ganesh is the form of the,

01:02:59.879 --> 01:03:05.374
you can say the purified
principle of the Earth element

01:03:05.733 --> 01:03:09.586
and is the same. I mean,

01:03:11.010 --> 01:03:18.195
in a flute you have two notes,

01:03:18.395 --> 01:03:24.067
the first and the last are the same.
In the same way in a human being the seven notes,

01:03:24.267 --> 01:03:27.437
the first one is
a Ganesha and the last one is also a Ganesha.

01:03:27.719 --> 01:03:30.167
So these seven notes are the same.

01:03:30.367 --> 01:03:38.048
And these seven notes make the Earth element

01:03:38.248 --> 01:03:44.988
and not completely Earth
element but started with earth element purified.

01:03:45.188 --> 01:03:48.358
When it loses its Earth
element problems completely

01:03:48.558 --> 01:03:51.695
it is Parabrahma, I mean it becomes all Brahma.

01:03:51.895 --> 01:03:58.902
Because Earth element is, outside is
the Earth element but inside is dhara,

01:03:59.102 --> 01:04:05.976
is dhara, is dharana – is the power
to sustain, is the power to sustain.

01:04:06.176 --> 01:04:11.114
And that power is the purest
form of Earth principle (tattwa).

01:04:12.948 --> 01:04:18.388
So, that you become later on; gradually the whole
Earth element drops down and you become that.

01:04:18.588 --> 01:04:22.726
So it is the dharana shakti as they
call it: the power of sustenance.

01:04:23.037 --> 01:04:26.008
Is the Ganesha.

01:04:27.032 --> 01:04:32.102
So, like that, in every chakra you have
a very subtle and subtle-most point.

01:04:32.302 --> 01:04:37.307
And that subtle-most point is the note that

01:04:37.825 --> 01:04:41.144
the Divine is playing at
that point, because every note

01:04:41.344 --> 01:04:45.908
has a different frequency, a
different intonation you can call it,

01:04:46.109 --> 01:04:51.755
a different sound, which helps
in the melody of this Universe.

01:04:53.026 --> 01:04:56.348
So, like that, we have seven chakras and the seven
notes.

01:04:56.549 --> 01:05:02.565
And they are different notes but these
notes then create permutations and combinations

01:05:02.765 --> 01:05:09.136
and that is how a chakra gets into a
swara (musical note) and then it becomes a

01:05:09.422 --> 01:05:14.444
a sound, and from a sound it becomes a word,
and from word it becomes a language and

01:05:14.644 --> 01:05:20.784
like that it goes on and the same subtle
form starts becoming something else.

01:05:20.984 --> 01:05:24.120
For example if I have love for my children:

01:05:24.320 --> 01:05:27.324
what, how I express it? I make a house for them,

01:05:27.524 --> 01:05:33.185
I make a place to live for them, I cook
food for them, I make a bed for them.

01:05:33.385 --> 01:05:36.452
It’s a gross expression
of that subtle love I have.

01:05:36.652 --> 01:05:40.805
In the same way whatever is subtle
within us is expressed outside

01:05:41.006 --> 01:05:44.216
with the help of the elements that are outside,

01:05:44.416 --> 01:05:51.203
to express the subtle through
our gross behaviour or gross

01:05:52.128 --> 01:05:54.844
material things also we do.

