have permanent residence. Some have bags full! You see.

01:09:47.316 --> 01:09:50.316
So you just can’t say what it will be.

01:10:11.647 --> 01:10:15.044
You just don’t worry about these things.

01:10:17.115 --> 01:10:22.819
You see the thing is people think that there’s only one
type of badha, emotional badha. There can be both types,

01:10:23.019 --> 01:10:28.190
a person who is very
egotistical also is dominated by somebody else.

01:10:28.391 --> 01:10:33.651
Abnormal area, abnormal behaviour, who
is not a normal person, can come from anywhere.

